&lt;h4 id=&#34;You-arenâ€™t-doing-Scrum-if-you-HAVE-to-work-more-than-40-hours-a-week&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#You-arenâ€™t-doing-Scrum-if-you-HAVE-to-work-more-than-40-hours-a-week&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;You arenâ€™t doing Scrum if you HAVE to work more than 40 hours a week.&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;You arenâ€™t doing Scrum if you HAVE to work more than 40 hours a week.&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;One of the benefits of Scrum is that it allows us to pace ourselves.Â  We no longer scramble to get stuff done.Â  We work consistently toward the goal.Â  But it isnâ€™t a race.&lt;/p&gt;
