&lt;p&gt;Now, why would we get a 404 error?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Well, the one place where this file wonâ€™t be available is when we are using &lt;code&gt;ng serve&lt;/code&gt; during development.  But when we load this with a regular server like Apache, IIS, or Nginx, the file will be available.&lt;/p&gt;
