&lt;h2 id=&#34;Design-Patterns&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Design-Patterns&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Design Patterns&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Design Patterns&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The more popular the design pattern, the more likely we are to see the exact same issues in our programming.Â  Currently, we can most clearly see this in the MV* design pattern.Â  Here again, people are using the design pattern based on what they imagine it to be. &lt;/p&gt;
