&lt;h2 id=&#34;Strong-Typing&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Strong-Typing&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Strong Typing&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Strong Typing&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;If youâ€™ve read any of my other post about Angular, youâ€™ll know Iâ€™m a very strong proponent of strongly typing everything.Â  Nowhere is this more useful than when creating the Effect chain.Â  By typing everything, I can easily tell that my code is written correctly.Â  Even while writing my book on how to get started with Angular, it has helped me figure out that Iâ€™m missing a closing bracket or parenthesis.Â  Not to mention it has told me exactly what block of code I had wrong.Â  Iâ€™ve probably saved hours of debugging time with this one simple enhancement to my coding practice.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;Chaining-Observables&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Chaining-Observables&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Chaining Observables&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Chaining Observables&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Iâ€™m almost ashamed to mention this next one.Â  But, I never really caught on that &lt;code&gt;switchMap()&lt;/code&gt; was a silent subscriber.Â  Oh! So many places you can use this. If youâ€™ve been using Effects, youâ€™ve probably seen code that looks like this:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&#34;highlight typescript&#34;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;gutter&#34;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;7&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;9&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;code&#34;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;meta&#34;&gt;@Effect&lt;/span&gt;()&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;attr&#34;&gt;get$&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span class=&#34;title class_&#34;&gt;Observable&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span class=&#34;title class_&#34;&gt;Edit&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span class=&#34;property&#34;&gt;Update&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; =&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;  &lt;span class=&#34;variable language_&#34;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span class=&#34;property&#34;&gt;actions$&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;Â  Â  .&lt;span class=&#34;title function_&#34;&gt;ofType&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span class=&#34;title class_&#34;&gt;Edit&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span class=&#34;property&#34;&gt;GET&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;Â  Â  .&lt;span class=&#34;title function_&#34;&gt;switchMap&lt;/span&gt;((&lt;span class=&#34;attr&#34;&gt;action&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&#34;title class_&#34;&gt;Edit&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span class=&#34;property&#34;&gt;Get&lt;/span&gt;): &lt;span class=&#34;title class_&#34;&gt;Observable&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;#123;&amp;#125; |&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;      &lt;span class=&#34;title class_&#3