&lt;h2 id=&#34;Fake-File-Upload&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Fake-File-Upload&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Fake File Upload&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Fake File Upload&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The only problem with this is that now we no longer have the file point, so if we want to upload the file, as a file, to the server we have come up with some way of creating a fake file object.Â  And believe it or not, that is a lot easier than you might think. &lt;/p&gt;
