&lt;p&gt;One is just plain arrogance.Â Being so sure you are right that you never stop to think you might be wrong.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I have to admit, when I first learned about immutability, I thought it sounded slow too. But, my thinking went along the lines of, â€œwell, much smarter people than me are working on this, they must think it makes sense. I wonder why?â€Â And then I started digging for answers.&lt;/p&gt;
