&lt;p&gt;To find the reasons why software architecture matters, it is helpful to think about what happens when there isnâ€™t any defined architecture in place.Â  For the purposes of this article, Iâ€™m going to generalize on how architecture impacts teams and where appropriate show why that is also important when your team is just you. &lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;/uploads/2017/02/image-1.png&#34; title=&#34;Reasons Software Architecture Matters&#34;&gt; Photo via &lt;a href=&#34;//visualhunt.com/&#34;&gt;VisualHunt&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
