&lt;h3 id=&#34;Lucky-People-Ask-Good-Questions&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Lucky-People-Ask-Good-Questions&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Lucky People Ask Good Questions&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Lucky People Ask Good Questions&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;It turns out that our brains answer any question we give it. In fact, youâ€™ve probably been in situations where someone has asked you a question you really didnâ€™t want to answer and youâ€™ve answered it anyhow. This is how compelling question are. &lt;/p&gt;
