&lt;h2 id=&#34;Hone-Your-Skills&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Hone-Your-Skills&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Hone Your Skills&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Hone Your Skills&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;One of the biggest frustrations I have is when I find someone â€œover 50â€ who has posted a comment saying he (most always it is a male) canâ€™t find a job because of age discrimination. I always wonder what skills he has, because where I live, weâ€™ll hire anyone who has an up to date skill set who can prove to us they really do know what they are doing. &lt;/p&gt;
