&lt;h2 id=&#34;Remember-whenâ€¦&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Remember-whenâ€¦&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Remember whenâ€¦&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Remember whenâ€¦&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Remember back to when AngularJS was first introduced?Â  The best platform we had at the time was jQuery and KnockOut.Â  Yes, there were others, but those were the most prominent.Â  Especially jQuery.Â  Since then, the browsers have stabilized and most of the reasons for using jQuery have vanished.&lt;/p&gt;
