&lt;p&gt;And then there is the history of various frameworks that have come out since.Â  Weâ€™ve made a lot of mistakes in the past that have led to improved ways of working with JavaScript to achieve various goals.Â  Function programming has crept into the mainstream.Â  Reactive programming has become more popular.&lt;/p&gt;
