&lt;p&gt;Drop into command line mode and run &lt;code&gt;ng test&lt;/code&gt; The first thing you will notice is that this brings up the Chrome browser to run your test. I donâ€™t know about you, but I really dislike having a browser window up. I have enough windows running on my screen as it is. This is the first thing we need to fix. To do this we are going to install PhantomJS.&lt;/p&gt;
