&lt;h3 id=&#34;Central-Source-of-Truth&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Central-Source-of-Truth&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Central Source of Truth&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Central Source of Truth&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Another place that needs to be addressed related to silos â€“ Another area that re-enforces and is a result of silos â€“ is this habit of each group using their own project management software.&lt;/p&gt;
