&lt;h2 id=&#34;Management-Doesnâ€™t-Like-the-Estimate&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Management-Doesnâ€™t-Like-the-Estimate&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Management Doesnâ€™t Like the Estimate&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Management Doesnâ€™t Like the Estimate&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;There have been a few times when the manager Iâ€™m working for doesnâ€™t like the estimate I provide.Â  In my experience there are several reasons for this.&lt;/p&gt;
