&lt;h2 id=&#34;Tools&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Tools&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Tools&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Tools&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;There are a couple of tools I really like for estimating.Â  The first one is the Mind Map.Â  If you arenâ€™t familiar with Mind Mapping, it is a way of just getting your ideas down on paper without having to worry about the structure or the order.Â  All you concentrate on is relationships.Â  This is a great way of breaking a project down into the smallest possible units of work.&lt;/p&gt;
