&lt;h2 id=&#34;Forget-Who-Is-Asking&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Forget-Who-Is-Asking&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Forget Who Is Asking&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Forget Who Is Asking&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Most people I work for give me pretty accurate descriptions of the problem Iâ€™m going to work on.Â  I can safely double the amount of time I think it will take and I generally hit my dates.&lt;/p&gt;
