&lt;h2 id=&#34;Step-7&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Step-7&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Step 7&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Step 7&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;There is one more possible problem we could encounter.Â  What if someone passes in a character that isnâ€™t a valid Roman number character.Â  We need to make sure that the only characters that show up are Roman number characters.&lt;/p&gt;
