&lt;h2 id=&#34;Step-8&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Step-8&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Step 8&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Step 8&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;OK. I think that gets all of the validations except for ensuring that the numbers show up in numerical order.Â  To make this work, we are going to need to work through the array and assign each digit a value.Â  The test we need to write is going to put values in the wrong order.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our test will put the next value up after the value.&lt;/p&gt;
